Rating: 3
I'm a vegetarian so I didn't eat any but my hubby says he loved it. He added quite a bit of vinegar. Also, I used whole grain melba toast from the grocery store instead of baking the Italian bread as a shortcut. The melba toast held the flavors well and did not get soggy. I think next time I might try Feta instead of the Mozzarella, which got lost in all the stronger flavors.

